    public class FNCImpl
extends SFImpl
implements FNC
    An implementation of the model object 'FNC'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Retired
    • Pat Tech
    • Reserved1
    • Fnt Flags
    • XUnit Base
    • YUnit Base
    • Xft Units
    • Yft Units
